### Head: Screenshot / Control
##
##
## ## Screenshot
## `Print`
##
Print
	scrot ~/pictures/screenshots/$(date +%Y%m%d)$(date +%H%M%S).png
##
## ## Screenshot Selected Area
## `Alt + Print`
##
alt + Print
	scrot -s ~/pictures/screenshots/$(date +%Y%m%d)$(date +%H%M%S).png
